Additional Term B: Prohibition on Improper Promotion & Defamation

This Website shall not be used by any person or entity for any illegal, fraudulent, defamatory, harassing, or any activity that may harm the reputation, brand, or trademarks of "Cait-Lab" or its owners. It is prohibited to imply sponsorship, endorsement, or affiliation with "Cait-Lab" or its owners when promoting or distributing this Website or derivative works, without their explicit written permission.

Additional Term C: Website Modification and Traceability Requirements

If the Website is modified, redeveloped or derivatively created, the modification records and the source of the original Website (indicating "Derived from Cait-Lab official website (https://Pu-94.github.io/cait-lab)") shall be marked in a prominent position of the Website. The copyright information and license terms of the original Website shall not be concealed, and the modified content shall comply with all conditions of this License.

Additional Term D: Data and Privacy Compliance Requirements

